## 11. Role Specification

### Full Stack Developer Responsibilities

- Frontend development (HTML, CSS, JavaScript, frameworks)  
- Backend development (server logic, APIs, databases)  
- Integration of frontend and backend systems  
- Performance optimization and security implementation  
- Deployment and maintenance support  

